COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1328 as follows:
1. On Page 1, Line 15, through Page 4, Line 23, by removing Section 1 and renumbering
subsequent sections;
2. On Page 5, Line 8, by striking after the word “is” and before the word “his”, the words
“separated from” and inserting the words “not currently in the legal custody of”;
3. On Page 5, Lines 9 through 10, by striking after the word “guardian” on Line 9 and before
the semicolon “;” on Line 10, all existing language and deleting all new language;
4. On Page 6, Line 17, by inserting after the word “in” and before the word “good”, the word
“reasonable”;
5. On Page 7, Line 23, by inserting after the comma “,”, the word “or”;
6. On Page 8, Lines 1 through 3, by deleting subparagraph b and renumbering the
subsequent subparagraph;
7. On Page 8, Lines 7 through 11, by deleting after the word “guardian” on Line 7 and
before the period “.” on Line 11, all new language; and
8. By amending the title to conform.
